jmf.discovery

Interface IPeerRegistry

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PeerRegistry

    public interface IPeerRegistry
    Data structure for the PeerRegistry which represents all known other peers in the system. Base class for PeerRegistryInternal. Created on 8/1/15.
    Author:
    Tobias Korb, Jonas Grunert
